'''Sicily Nation''' ({{lang-it|Sicilia Nazione}}, '''SN''') is a [[separatism|separatist]] [[list of political parties in Italy|Italian political party]] active in [[Sicily]].
The party was founded in January 2015 by [[Gaetano Armao]], a former regional minister of Economy under President [[Raffaele Lombardo]], and [[Rino Piscitello]], a long-time politician ([[Proletarian Unity Party (Italy)|Proletarian Unity Party]], [[Proletarian Democracy]], [[The Network (political party)|The Network]], [[The Democrats (Italy)|The Democrats]], [[Democracy is Freedom – The Daisy|Democracy is Freedom]], [[Democratic Party (Italy)|Democratic Party]]) who had lately been the secretary of Lombardo's [[Party of Sicilians]]. The party aimed at the transformation of Sicily into a nation confederated to Italy or an independent country.<ref>http://livesicilia.it/2015/01/16/armao-fonda-sicilia-nazione-contro-lo-scippo-dellautonomia_587059</ref><ref>http://giornalelora.com/politica/nasce-sicilia-nazione-con-armao-e-piscitello</ref>
In January 2017 SN was a founding member of the [[Sicilian National Movement]] (MNS), along with the [[Sicilian Independence Movement]] (re-edition of the separatist party which was active after [[World War II]]) and the [[Sicilian National Front]].<ref>http://www.liberoquotidiano.it/news/politica/12279089/sicilia-nasce-il-movimento-nazionale-siciliano-e-candida-alla-regione-gaetano-armao.html</ref> The MNS supported Armao for [[President of Sicily]] in the [[Sicilian regional election, 2017|2017 regional election]].<ref>http://palermo.repubblica.it/dettaglio-news/-/4681510</ref>
==Leadership== *Coordinator: [[Gaetano Armao]] (2015–present) *Members of the National Committee: [[Gaetano Armao]] (2015–present), [[Massimo Costa]] (2015), [[Rino Piscitello]] (2015–present)
